    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "The Spokane Township clubs will\ncome together again September 8\nat the Spokane county courthouse\nfor the purpose of looking over\ngrand jury prospects in the county\ninvestigation. and generally\nstrengthening their organization.\nThe grand jury reconvenes Septem-\nDer l. at which time Deputy Prose-\ncutor Donovan will be ready with\nthe results Of the special work of\ninvestigation that the grand jury\nrequested him to perform during\nthe recess.\n\n\nLeading men Of the state will\nattend the township club meeting\nand speak. Among them will be\nc. B. Kegley, grand master of the\nstate grange, and State Organizer\nReed of the Farmers union."
    }
